'''''Leski Auctions: Sport and General Memorabilia, 10th February 2005''''' is an auction catalogue from Charles Leski Auctions. The description for Lot 72 includes a full reproduction (photographs) of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]'s [[Letter to Mrs Souch|letter to Mr(s?) Souch (8 September 1955)]].
